Package fr.anthonyrey.activities

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    BackgroundService
    This class is to be only instantiated with > 16 api It creates an intentService which handle the notifications about tickets
    Cloture
    This class is an android Activity, it allows you to close a ticket and eventually give a solution to it
    InfosTicket
    This class is an android Activity, it shows the details of the ticket you selected
    Listing
    This class is an android Activity, here you can select a ticket from the list
    Login
    This class is an android Activity, it is the class being reached each time the application starts and it also puts in place the storage in order to keep sessions related data between intents.
